                "descriptions": [
                    {
                        "id": 25,
                        "text": "Since 1991, Hitech Corp has been your trusted partner in providing complete packaging solutions. We offer a wide range of rigid plastic packaging with unique designs which are tailor-made for your requirements. From ideation to prototyping to manufacturing to final delivery of the product, we closely collaborate with you all the way."
                    },
