                        "id": 26,
                        "text": "To meet our customer requirements of speed to market, we have 13 manufacturing facilities across India and a state-of-the-art technology centre. We serve a diverse array of industries, from personal care to home care, food & beverages to dairy, paints to oils and lubricants, and agrochemicals to pharmaceuticals."
